title: Magic.2015.Language.Selector-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:


                        Magic 2015 *Language Selector*

    Release Date :  7/2014                         Protection : Brains
    Discs        :  0.1                            Genre      : RPG


  This is a language selector for our main release: Magic 2015


   - Extract
   - Run language selector
   - Select desired language and hit install button
   - Play

   Notes: Theyre 9 available languages to select:
          - English
		  - German
		  - French
		  - Italian
		  - Spanish
		  - Portuguese
		  - Korean
		  - Japanese
		  - Russian
		  You can change the language through selector at any time.


                       CODEX is currently looking for:

                          nothing but competition!

                              are you ready?

       LNK^CPS                                                02/2014
